OL,3,CAmbulance staff abused and attacked
OL,4,Cdaily
OL,6,FAmbulance staff in the South Central
OL,7,Fregion are experiencing daily physical
OL,8,Fand verbal abuse as attacks reach
OL,9,Frecord highs.
OL,11,FSouth Central Ambulance Service NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust (SCAS) said at least
OL,13,Fthree members of staff were abused or
OL,14,Fattacked every day, with an average of
OL,15,Fjust over 95 incidents recorded every
OL,16,Fmonth in the past year.
