OL,6,FNational figures show that from April
OL,7,F2024 to March 2025, the highest rate
OL,8,Fof reported incidents of violence,
OL,9,Faggression and abuse ` 22,536 ` was
OL,10,Frecorded against ambulance service
OL,11,Fstaff; an increase of almost 15% on
OL,12,Fthe previous year.
OL,14,FThe incidents reported included
OL,15,Fkicking, punching, slapping, head-
OL,16,Fbutting, spitting, verbal abuse and
OL,17,Fsexual assault, and ranged from common
OL,18,Fassault to significant serious attacks
OL,19,Finvolving a multitude of weapons.
