OL,6,FStudent paramedic, Al Goffey, was
OL,7,Fattacked in Aylesbury by a patient
OL,8,Fthat had flagged down his ambulance.
OL,9,FHis attacker was sentenced to 18
OL,10,Fmonths for assault.
OL,12,FSCAS is supporting the calls made
OL,13,Ftoday (24 April, 2025) by the
OL,14,FAssociation of Ambulance Chief
OL,15,FExecutives (AACE) for further national
OL,16,Fpolicy interventions to help combat
OL,17,Fthe growing number of violent assaults
OL,18,Fagainst ambulance workers in the UK.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
