OL,6,FCommenting on the latest figures,
OL,7,FKirsten Willis-Drewett, assistant
OL,8,Fdirector or operations at SCAS, said:
OL,10,F"Unfortunately we know that staff out
OL,11,Fon the road and in our control room
OL,12,Fface unacceptable physical and verbal
OL,13,Fabuse every day, and we wholeheartedly
OL,14,Fsupport AACE's calls for more action
OL,15,Fto address this rising problem.
OL,26,@rD@AOU
