OL,6,FThe data from AACE ` which represents
OL,7,Fthe UK public ambulance sector `
OL,8,Freveals that the summer months were
OL,9,Fwhen the most incidents of violence
OL,10,Fand aggression were reported, with
OL,11,Fsummer 2024 recording the highest
OL,12,Fnumber of incidents on record, with
OL,13,F6,093 reported.
OL,15,FAmbulance leaders also said many
OL,16,Fincidents go unreported meaning the
OL,17,Factual figure could be much higher.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
