OL,6,FOfficials said some serious attacks
OL,7,Fhad involved "a multitude of weapons"
OL,8,Fand alcohol was a "prominent factor"
OL,9,Fin a number of attacks.
OL,11,FDrugs, mental health issues, race and
OL,12,Fsexuality have also been listed as
OL,13,Ffactors in the attacks.
OL,15,FAACE chair, Jason Killens, said: "This
OL,16,Fsituation is now so serious that we
OL,17,Fare seeking to engage with UK health
OL,18,Fministers at the highest level to
OL,19,Fexplore new interventions that could
OL,20,Fhelp deter potential perpetrators of
OL,21,Fthese attacks.
