OL,6,F"We would also underline again that it
OL,7,Fis vital that the judiciary uses all
OL,8,Favailable legislation to ensure
OL,9,Fappropriate sentences are handed out
OL,10,Fconsistently to those found guilty of
OL,11,Fcommitting these horrific crimes
OL,12,Fagainst our workforce."
OL,14,FSaffron Cordery, interim chief
OL,15,Fexecutive, NHS Providers, said:
OL,16,F"Ambulance and NHS staff doing their
OL,17,Fbest for patients must be able to go
OL,18,Fabout their often life-saving work
OL,19,Fwithout fear of attack.
