OL,6,F"Staff safety is a top priority for
OL,7,FNHS trust leaders. There must be zero
OL,8,Ftolerance for any violence or
OL,9,Faggression against NHS workers."
OL,11,FA UK Government spokesperson said that
OL,12,F"violence of any kind is
OL,13,Funacceptable", adding: "The Government
OL,14,Ftakes a zero-tolerance approach to
OL,15,Fthis type of behaviour and those who
OL,16,Fassault emergency workers can face up
OL,17,Fto two years' imprisonment.
